original_title: Jeff "Big Daddy" Wayne: Big Daddy Kicks It
overview: Comedian Jeff Wayne was dubbed “Big Daddy” by Billy Crystal and Robin Williams on an HBO Comic Relief show. The moniker has stuck to a guy who’s been part of the stand-up comedy scene for a long time. He’s toured all over the world, several times in Europe. The Norwegian Newspaper “Sondags B.A.”, described him as having “amazing audience communication, and ferociously funny!” ​
title: Jeff "Big Daddy" Wayne: Big Daddy Kicks It
